Tr%E1%BB%A9/poem-NrIIAlUplVGXQz8y0KLfkA">Tiễn trí sự kinh doãn Nguyễn Công Trứ - 餞致事京尹阮公著</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Kh%E1%BA%A3i/author-lfkyiRMg6zwt6_eiwas6Yg">Vũ Phạm Khải</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/T%E1%BB%91ng-b%E1%BA%AFc-s%E1%BB%A9-Ma-H%E1%BB%A3p-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C3%A3ng/poem-1_gzqBpaWCQxref92p7EeA">Tống bắc sứ Ma Hợp, Kiều Nguyên Lãng - 送北使麻合，喬元郎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Nh%C3%A2n-T%C3%B4ng/author-EY7jN0xHQfiiJpD91KwIgw">Trần Nhân Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Tr%E1%BA%A7m-t%C6%B0-m%E1%BA%A1n-th%C3%A0nh/poem-JNIPlA0tbkXxy-0mWrgQKA">Trầm tư mạn thành - 沉思谩成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%B4n-Ch%C3%ADnh/V%E1%BB%8B-Kh%C3%AA-x%C3%A3-hoa-th%C3%B4n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-hJ6AGDtZrq76iaGCIQT6Yg">Vị Khê xã hoa thôn từ - 渭溪社花村祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%C3%B4n-Ch%C3%ADnh/author-hgCHpxJ-0-MCH2PIU-32Hw">Phạm Đôn Chính</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
